  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to collect data to confirm the safety and effectiveness of
      the ImageReady™ MR Conditional Defibrillation System when used in the 1.5T MRI environment
      under the labeled Conditions of Use
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
